12. Be3
12. Be6( 12...Nd4 { would be a strategic mistake after }13.Bxd4 exd4 14.Nb5 c5 15.b4! { putting immediate pressure. }15...a6 16.Nd6!! { and Black's center falls apart. } )
13. Nd2{ White's knight eyes the most aspiring  c5 -square. }
