16. Qb6
17. e4{ We keep the Bishops and prepare  Rac1 - Be3 . }
17. e5
18. Be3
18. Qxd6
19. Rfd1
19. Qc6
20. Rac1{ White has compensation, as he will soon open the position and the Bishops will have more power. For example: }
