6. Rb1
6. a5{ Stopping  b2 - b4 . The difference between this system and the Vigorito line with  e7 - e5 , is that Black's later  d7 - d5  will be weaker and White can try to prepare  d2 - d4 , too. }
7. d3{ It's important to start with this move, as we want to build our  Bd2 - Qc1  battery quickly. }
