8. Bd2
8. Nge7
9. h4{ before building the  Bd2 - Qc1  battery, we ask questions with  h4 . }
9. h6( 9...h5?! { would be strategically dubious, as after }10.Nh3 { White would have great squares for the pieces. } )
10. Qc1
10. b6{ Black has to develop somehow. }( 10...Nd4 { could be simply answered with }11.b3 { and later the Knight can be kicked with  e2 - e3 . } )
11. Nf3
11. Bb7
12. O-O{ White has a better position and an easy plan of  Nb5 - b4 . }
