22. Nf3{ After the massive exchanges, White has a Rook and a pawn for the Queen. Nevertheless, the  f5  pawn is very weak and probably will be collected with  Bh3 - Nh4  in the future. Also, White is quite safe in the long run, as the pieces are quite compact. }
