8. Na6{ Black has to protect it with this awkward looking move. }
9. Rc1
9. Nd7( 9...Qc7 10.Qd2 O-O 11.b4 { Black is under serious pressure. } )
10. h4{ I would not hurry with  Nf3 , as Black is stuck and can't play  b6 . White can improve the position with  a2 - a3 ,  Qa4 , preparing  b2 - b4 . }
