5. b4{ After analyzing several lines, I think it's best to take the opportunity to take space on the queenside right now. }
5. a5
6. b5
6. Ne4{ The critical approach. }
7. Qc2
7. Nxc3
8. Bb2{ This is the point. By playing 5.b4, we are in time to meet  Ne4  with this thematic pattern. Once White will recapture on  c3  with a piece, the space advantage on the queenside will be consolidated. }
