19. Qb3{ White won the battle for the key squares, and goes for the  b7 -pawn. }
19. Rd7
20. Rb1
20. e4{ A desperate attempt to create counterplay. Eventually the weakened Black King will also play an important role. }
21. dxe4
21. Rf8
22. e3
